# Seer-Core Workspace Agent Instructions

Please read the instructions inside `.cursorrules` to orient yourself with this repository.

Key Tasks & Discovery:
- Setup command: `npm run setup` (runs compilation and builds initial index database).
- Reference specs:
  - Architectural & Product Spec: `seer-master-guide.md`
  - Developer & Testing Spec: `README_dev.md`
  - CLI & MCP Reference Guide: `seer-cli-docs.md`
- Run core tests: `npm test`
- Verify optimizations: `npm run test:mcp` (verifies token budget, did-you-mean suggestions, structural skeletons, batches, and traces).
